  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/b0adba1c39947b653eb1927e8173ad29.poster.avif?t=1724844648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/b0adba1c39947b653eb1927e8173ad29.webm?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/b0adba1c39947b653eb1927e8173ad29.mp4?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Neon Phonk Robots is a game for true connoisseurs of Phonk and its aesthetics. Immerse yourself in the dynamic atmosphere of this music, enjoy the light of bright neon, and blow up more robots!<br><br><strong>Buying drones</strong><br>You can buy armed robots! Assemble your own squad of mechanical companions. Do you like to tear and throw? Create a crowd of stormtroopers! Do you prefer to destroy enemies at a distance? A crowd of long-range robots will help you with this! Do you consider yourself smarter than others and want to make a balanced squad? As your heart desires!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/d525ab648b8f514f7831cca1d38bba74.poster.avif?t=1724844648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/d525ab648b8f514f7831cca1d38bba74.webm?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/d525ab648b8f514f7831cca1d38bba74.mp4?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>A variety of weapons</strong><br>You can buy new guns! Tired of blowing up robots with a submachine gun? Buy a rifle! And then there's the acid cannon, and a couple of machine guns! And go blow up the robots!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/c7eb66f4e99c7e706df8878713d1d6ec.poster.avif?t=1724844648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/c7eb66f4e99c7e706df8878713d1d6ec.webm?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/c7eb66f4e99c7e706df8878713d1d6ec.mp4?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Capturing and strengthening points</strong><br>You can capture points and buy turrets! Have you captured a point? Well done, and now install a healthy neon turret on it! So that everyone knows that this is your point, and you will not give it to anyone!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/a2cca8b87ef0d8748a0461927bc70086.poster.avif?t=1724844648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/a2cca8b87ef0d8748a0461927bc70086.webm?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/a2cca8b87ef0d8748a0461927bc70086.mp4?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Specific design</strong><br>Neon, neon, more neon! The game literally glows like Tokyo at night! Everything is glowing! Walls, graffiti, robots, guns, bullets, everything!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/8e7a5c1675fe87947a75d70ad6563b97.poster.avif?t=1724844648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/8e7a5c1675fe87947a75d70ad6563b97.webm?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/8e7a5c1675fe87947a75d70ad6563b97.mp4?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Unique tracks</strong><br>What is the best thing to listen to when you blow up robots - of course Phonk. And what's the best thing to do when listening to Phonk? Blow up robots!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/81a3080d279d5b6dafde4eee135e55d7.poster.avif?t=1724844648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/81a3080d279d5b6dafde4eee135e55d7.webm?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/81a3080d279d5b6dafde4eee135e55d7.mp4?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>What are you waiting for? Turn on the phonk to the maximum and run to the neon city, blow up robots, in Neon Phonk Robots!!!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/10025e6dc88d14f0a1e99f69dcc98123.poster.avif?t=1724844648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/10025e6dc88d14f0a1e99f69dcc98123.webm?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/10025e6dc88d14f0a1e99f69dcc98123.mp4?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
